-- Tullett Said to Hire Chillington for Alternative Investments
-- B y   W e n d y   M o c k
-- 2012-05-10T07:33:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-10/tullett-said-to-hire-chillington-for-alternative-investments.html
Tullett Prebon Plc (TLPR) , a London-based
diversified inter-dealer broker, hired Tim Chillington as a
manager of alternative investments in Hong Kong, according to a
person familiar with the matter.  Chillington will cover Asia secondary loans trading and
began his new role on May 2, the person said. He was previously
head of secondary loans and illiquid broking at  GFI Group Inc. (GFIG) 
in Hong Kong, the person said.  A Tullett Prebon spokeswoman in London, Charlotte Kirkham,
